cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on meta-learning for few-shot learning, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper specifically deals with image classification tasks, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.CV.
